      starterCode: "#include <cstdio>\n#include <cmath>\n\nstruct Vec2 { float x; float y; };\nstruct Entity { Vec2 pos; Vec2 vel; Vec2 half; };\n\n// TODO: 写 overlaps(const Entity& a, const Entity& b)，返回 bool\n// 提示：两轴的中心距都小于半宽之和才算相交\n\nint main() {\n    Entity a{{0, 0}, {0, 0}, {10, 10}};\n    Entity b{{15, 0}, {0, 0}, {10, 10}};\n    printf(\"%d\\n\", overlaps(a, b) ? 1 : 0);\n    return 0;\n}\n",
      hints: ["AABB 即轴对齐包围盒，half.x、half.y 是矩形从中心到边的距离。", "X 轴相交条件：|a.pos.x - b.pos.x| < a.half.x + b.half.x。", "两轴必须同时满足才算真的碰上，用 && 连接。"],
